  can be added in the name field. The format for name must be like: '<i>testName:propertyName:mode</i>' (without quotes).
  For eg. to add a property <i>abc</i> for a test named <i>test1</i> and mode <i>b</i>, input: <i>test1:abc:b</i> in the name field.

